t different spectral\nhardness and one has to study both the spectral as well as rapid variability to\nidentify this unusual state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 17:08:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 15:35:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
