od, which\nshows that tremendous edge computing performance improvement can be achieved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 19:28:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 May 2017 03:42:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-15"}
