)$. Our results give a comprehensive picture of angular\nmomentum transport of the MRI with an imposed azimuthal field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2017 14:11:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Oct 2017 20:37:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-21"}
